Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the dynamic interactions for the connectivity behavior of the gke-pubsub-websocket-adapter system:

```plantuml
@startuml GoogleCloudPlatform_gke-pubsub-websocket-adapter

participant "Pub/Sub Topic" as PubSub
participant "pulltop" as Pulltop
participant "Ephemeral Storage" as Storage
participant "websocketd" as Websocketd
participant "WebSocket Client" as Client

PubSub -> Pulltop: Publish message
Pulltop -> Storage: Store message
Pulltop -> Websocketd: Notify new message

Client -> Websocketd: Connect
Websocketd -> Storage: Retrieve recent messages
Storage --> Websocketd: Return messages
Websocketd -> Client: Send initial messages

loop Message streaming
    PubSub -> Pulltop: Publish new message
    Pulltop -> Storage: Store new message
    Pulltop -> Websocketd: Notify new message
    Websocketd -> Client: Stream new message
end

@enduml
```